snippet.title: Black Matrix 00 PS1 Game Intro Movie HQ
snippet.description:
Opening movie of the PS1 game Black Matrix 00, a good tactical RPG that was only released in Japan.

Intro del juego de PS1 Black Matrix 00, un buen tactico RPG que sólo salió en Japón.

Game copyright: NEC Interchannel (2004)

More information about the game here:
http://www.psxdatacenter.com
